1. The required documents for a tourist visa application for Taiwanese passport holders
2. The application process (in-person appointment, online, or by mail)
3. Processing time and visa fees
4. Whether I can apply directly at the Consulate in Buenos Aires

I appreciate your time and look forward to your response.

